  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "On that bright and golden morning",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the Son of Man shall come,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And the radiance of His glory we shall see;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When from ev'ry clime and nation",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He shall call His people home,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 25
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring of the ransomed that will be!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 43
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "CHORUS",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring, what a gath'ring,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 25
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring of the ransomed in the summer land of love!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 55
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring, what a gath'ring,"
    }, {
      "text" : "Of the ransomed in that happy home above.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 36
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "When the blest, who sleep in Jesus,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 29
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "at His bidding shall arise",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "From the silence of the grave, and from the sea,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And with bodies all celestial they shall meet Him in the skies,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 57
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring and rejoicing there will be!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "When our eyes behold the city, with its many mansions bright,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 25
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 40
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 54
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And its river, calm and restful, flowing free;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the friends that death hath parted shall in bliss again unite,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 33
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 49
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 62
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a gath'ring and a greeting there will be!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 43
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 4",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "O the King is surely coming, and the time is drawing nigh,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 37
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 53
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When the blessèd day of promise we shall see;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Then the changing in a moment, in the twinkling of an eye,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 54
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And forever in His presence we shall be.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
